### Admin login
POST http://localhost:4060/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"email": "admin@mail",
	"password": "admin"
}

### Check current auth (confirms ADMIN token cookie)
GET http://localhost:4060/auth/check-auth

### Read all users and authors
GET http://localhost:4060/admin-api/users

### Block a user/author
PATCH http://localhost:4060/admin-api/users/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"userId": "PUT_USER_OR_AUTHOR_ID_HERE",
	"isUserActive": false
}

### Activate a user/author
PATCH http://localhost:4060/admin-api/users/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
	"userId": "PUT_USER_OR_AUTHOR_ID_HERE",
	"isUserActive": true
}

### Admin logout
GET http://localhost:4060/auth/logout

